 4. Core Responsibilities

4.1 Value Measurement

- Quantifies real economic contribution
- Filters spam and fake activity

---

4.2 Value Distribution

- Allocates rewards based on contribution
- Protects early pioneers

---

4.3 Liquidity Stabilization

- Monitors system health (Φ)
- Adjusts incentives dynamically

---

4.4 Incentive Alignment

- Ensures:
  - Honest behavior → rewarded
  - Exploitation → penalized

---

---

